The '''Black Sea field mouse''' (''Apodemus ponticus'')  is a species of [[rodent]] in the family [[Muridae]].
It is found in [[Armenia]], [[Azerbaijan]], [[Georgia (country)|Georgia]], possibly [[Iran]], [[Iraq]], [[Russian Federation]], and [[Turkey]].

