{{Politics of Burkina Faso}}
'''Parliamentary elections''' were held in [[Burkina Faso]] on 6 May 2007.<ref name=IPU>[http://www.ipu.org/parline-e/reports/arc/2047_07.htm Elections in 2007] IPU</ref> The result was a victory for the ruling [[Congress for Democracy and Progress]] (CDP), which won 73 of the 111 seats in the [[National Assembly of Burkina Faso|National Assembly]].
