{{Infobox diocese |jurisdiction = Diocese |name = Dundo |latin = Dioecesis Dundensis |country = {{flag|Angola}} |metropolitan = [[Roman Catholic Archdiocese of Saurímo|Saurímo]] |rite = [[Latin Rite]] |cathedral = Sé Catedral de Nossa Senhora da Conceiçao |cocathedral = |area_km2 = |population = |population_as_of = |catholics = |catholics_percent= |pope = {{Incumbent pope}} |bishop = |coadjutor = |auxiliary_bishops= }}
